text: Aurore Sacré (born on April 13, 1993 in Saint-Jean-d'Angély) is a French water polo player. She competed with the French women's national water polo team at the 2014 European Women's Water Polo Championship, the 2015 Women's World Water Polo Championship, and the 2016 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2016 FINA Women's Water Polo World League, and 2017 Women's World Water Polo Championship. She plays at the Angers Nautic Club. == References == == Other websites== *EspritBleu *French Swimming Federation *Swimrankings Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players Category:Sportspeople from Nouvelle-Aquitaine Category:People from Charente-Maritime
